http://www.aaii.org:80/glossary.html 206.30.246.237 19970111222432 text/html 24385
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 11-Jan-97 22:27:23 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 12-Jun-96 01:13:26 GMT
