<P>
<B><FONT SIZE=+1>INTRODUCTION </FONT></B>: 
<P>
Market studies calculate value assessments with the accuracy of information
made known to the writing team. They in turn point to probable and quantifiable
markets. Very seldom does a product present itself that has a market beyond
the scope of normal business parameters. 
<P>
In the final analysis, numerous colossal markets were identified for the
products that Remedial Air Systems INC. could introduce globally.
<P>
<P>
The products from Remedial Air Systems are a new branch of an existing
technology. Their succinct purpose is to bring the healthy conditions of
natural outdoor air ; by replicating nature's methods ; indoors. That is
what this study, in distinction, is all about. The supporting information
clearly shows that there is a specific market that Remedial Air Systems Inc.
will have at its command. 
<P>
We invite you to read the study in it's entirety and come to your own conclusions
about the new products that Remedial Air Systems will advance as to their
likelihood of being a boon to society. We also boldly state that if Remedial
Air Systems follow their perquisite path of action, then the company stands
a far above average prospect of becoming a World Leader for this burgeoning
new product technology !
<P>
<P ALIGN=Center>
  <HR>
