<H1 ALIGN=Center>
  Labor Day Products
</H1>
<P ALIGN=Center>
<B><IMG SRC="top10.gif" WIDTH="80" HEIGHT="89"></B>
<P ALIGN=Left>
<B>As summer draws to a muggy close, Labor Day will soon be here. Every year
on this holiday, families from all across the country come together to celebrate
the working men and women who continually make us proud to be a part of this
great nation. We at the Made in the USA Foundation salute these Americans,
who take pride in their work and in the goods that they produce.</B>
<P ALIGN=Left>
<B>Below you'll find a descriptions of some of the finest products made in
the United States. Some you'll find useful for family picnics or when the
children return to school. Others include stories of companies founded on
an American Dream, which says that with perserverance, anything is possible.
Yet, all the products listed below share one thing in common: they are made
by the hands of dedicated American men and women. </B>
<P ALIGN=Left>
<B>Happy Labor Day America!</B>
<P>
<P>
  <HR>
