  <HR>
</B><FONT SIZE=+1> </FONT>
<H2>
  <A NAME=tool><B><FONT SIZE=+1>American Tool
  Company</FONT></B></A><FONT SIZE=+1> </FONT>
</H2>
<P>
<B><FONT SIZE=+1>The American Tool Company manufactures all of its excellent
hand tools in the United States, mostly in Lincoln, Nebraska. American Tool
offers <I>Vise-Grip </I>locking pliers and specialty locking tools,
<I>Quick-Grip </I>one-handed bar clamps, <I>Unibit</I> step drills,
<I>Prosnip</I> tin and aviation snips and <I>Chesco </I>hex key sets. All
of these tools pass a rigid factory inspection and carry a full warranty
against defects in materials and workmanship.</FONT></B><FONT SIZE=+1> </FONT>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=+1> </FONT>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=+1> </FONT>
